data.description: One of a kind farmhouse in Kenton on a huge lot! Live out your homesteading dreams or build your future ADU. The possibilities are endless.  This house features big windows, skylights galore, high ceilings, exposed beams, amazing natural light, wide open floor plan and beautiful wood floors. Great home for hosting parties and events. 3 beds up with bonus room in primary. 4th bed on main doubles as office. So much room to spread out and enjoy. Many updates including new interior + exterior paint, AC, new gutters, new windows and french drain.  Huge yard with fig, plum + cherry trees, raised garden beds, grapevines + room for RV parking. Quick stroll to Kenton Park, Posies, Kenton Club and the Kenton Farmer's Market.  This is a must see! [Home Energy Score = 1. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10226804]
